@startuml repositorypatternimplementation-architecture
!include ../../../docs/puml/_standard-style.puml

title Repository Pattern Implementation - Architecture Overview

package "Application Layer" {
  [Service] as Service
  [Use Cases] as UseCases
}

package "Domain Layer" {
  [IRepository] as IRepo
  [Entity] as Entity
  [Value Objects] as VO
}

package "Infrastructure Layer" {
  [Repository Implementation] as RepoImpl
  [Database Adapter] as DBAdapter
  database "GraphDB + LevelDB" as DB
}

Service --> UseCases
UseCases --> IRepo
IRepo <|.. RepoImpl
RepoImpl --> DBAdapter
DBAdapter --> DB

note right of IRepo
  **Repository Contract:**
  - Abstract data access
  - Domain-focused interface
  - Technology agnostic
end note

note right of RepoImpl
  **Concrete Implementation:**
  - GraphDB integration
  - LevelDB persistence
  - Query optimization
end note

@enduml
